{"name":"Token","type":"asset","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":"<div style=\"mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\nmso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 0in 1.0pt 0in\"><p class=\"ThemepackHeader2\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:7.0pt;\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><em>Link to your occupation</em></span></p></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-no-proof:yes\">This asset exemplifies the success or authority of your occupation.</span></p>","value":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.WqhyhzpnO99xZ8YR"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"nova6","systemVersion":"0.1.20","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1670794368458,"modifiedTime":1673855981046,"lastModifiedBy":"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY"},"ownership":{"default":0,"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"4Obp1Ves0PI7Q1sd"}
{"name":"Memento","type":"asset","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":"<div style=\"mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\nmso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 0in 1.0pt 0in\"><p class=\"ThemepackHeader2\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:7.0pt;\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><em>Keepsake connected to your past</em></span></p></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-no-proof:yes\">This is connected</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">  </span>to your background or trouble that you value above more than anything <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.3pt\">(except, maybe, your treasured possession).</span></p>","value":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.nova6-beyond-hope-and-reason.Pdr3l8coZ38XZnZ2"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"nova6","systemVersion":"0.1.20","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1670794449177,"modifiedTime":1673855973165,"lastModifiedBy":"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY"},"ownership":{"default":0,"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"DIhjTVLoxWetHutb"}
{"name":"The Unreal","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":"<p>The Unreal reflects your understanding of things you were not meant to know—the horrible truth that lies behind what nearly everyone believes to be real. Folk without skill in The Unreal are referred to, respectfully, as the oblivious. In the context of the Unreal, Reality is what the oblivious believe, perceive, and experience to be the truth of the cosmos.</p><div><h1>Unreal Insight</h1></div><p>Insights into the truth of the cosmos can provide a +1d bonus in any action test when you spend one point of Unreal Insight. However, your approach will possibly frighten any oblivious who witness your action.</p><h2>Knowing The Unreal</h2><p>When you suffer a grave aspect when confronted by the Unreal or gain Unreal Insight, you can spend one Plot Point to gain one rank (and one only) in The Unreal that will last until the next major milestone. Optionally, you can increase the duration of the grave aspect by one step instead of spending the Plot Point.</p><div><h1>The Unreal Subverts Reality</h1></div><p>The Unreal responds to your will, which is not the same as submitting to your will. You can spend a Plot Point to subvert reality and use The Unreal to create almost any kind of effect. Failure is…not good.</p><p>Those souls that figured out some amount of control with consistency of outcome, survived, and then thought to share their discovery recorded their success as a spell to be studied and mastered.</p><div><h1>The Unreal Reveals Terrifying Truth</h1></div><p>Use The Unreal to create advantage when solving eldritch puzzles, learning spells, or confronting the Unreal. This can be used to reduce the time required or increase the value of success.</p><h2>Such Terrible Knowledge</h2><p>Wits can never provide understanding, but it can be used to translate the Unreal in a way that is useful to the oblivious. This could be a Challenge or a Conflict and require a scene or more. Regardless, each failure results in damage 2 [T] mental (fear). Success solves the puzzle or learns the spell.</p><h2>Recognizing The Unreal</h2><p>You can also use the Unreal to identify eldritch terrors from their spoor, possibly discern details about how to serve or banish such terrors, or recognize otherwise hidden evidence of the Unreal.</p>","rank":0,"focused":false,"practiced":false,"specialized":false,"perk1":"","perk2":"","perk3":"","perk4":"","perk5":"","perk6":"","perk7":"","perk8":"","perk9":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.nova6-skills.dVXCE5GU33h7dw1l"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"nova6","systemVersion":"0.1.20","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1670793433456,"modifiedTime":1673855979207,"lastModifiedBy":"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY"},"ownership":{"default":0,"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"LuNwO65fYiGLOZZz"}
{"name":"Occupation","type":"aspect","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":"<p><em>Replaces High Concept</em></p><hr><p>Your occupation provides you with resources, knowledge, privilege, responsibility, and complications. Examples:</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpFirst\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Alienist</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> Who are we to the cosmos?</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Antiquarian</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> History is experienced through the artifacts of history.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Archeologist</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> Our world is built on the bones of prior worlds.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Athlete</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> For the love of the game—and to win.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Author</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> The human condition is endless, storied emotion.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Criminal</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> Laws keep the sheep in the pen—and I’m a wolf.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Detective/PI</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> Money or love—either is the likely solve.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Dilettante</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> There is so much to do, and money is no object.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Devout</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> I bring hope and restore faith.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Doctor of Medicine.</span> I hold special obligations to all my fellow human beings, those sound of mind and body as well as the infirm.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Engineer</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> Society is built on my vision and skill.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Entertainer</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> All the world’s a stage.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Explorer</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> Into parts unknown with so much of the world to see.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Heir</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> You can get more money, but you cannot get more time. <span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\"> </span></p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Journalist</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> There’s always more to the story, and I always find it.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Lawyer</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> The code we live by defines our society.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Librarian</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> The catalog of human knowledge is bounded infinity.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Military Officer</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> I lead forces into the very mouth of hell.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Pilot</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> I use my knowledge to thwart nature.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Police Officer</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> Protect and serve.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Professional</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> Money makes the world go ‘round.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Professor</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> You are an expert in your field and in teaching others.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Psychoanalyst</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> <span style=\"letter-spacing:-.3pt\">You meet your destiny on the road you take to avoid it.</span></p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Scientist</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> I use my knowledge to thwart nature.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpLast\"><span style=\"font-size:\n11.0pt\">Soldier</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">.</strong> I am the first through the breach and last line of defense.</p>","text":"","label":"Occupation","invoked":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.nova6-beyond-hope-and-reason.Ac5CMHlHWspXpG1t"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"nova6","systemVersion":"0.1.20","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1670794171843,"modifiedTime":1673855974564,"lastModifiedBy":"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY"},"ownership":{"default":0,"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"MxAQef9ttdcK3jFL"}
{"name":"Trappings","type":"asset","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":"<div style=\"mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\nmso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 0in 1.0pt 0in\"><p class=\"ThemepackHeader2\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:7.0pt;\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><em>Things associated with your occupation</em></span></p></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\">You are assumed to have all the essential items for livelihood and your occupation. This includes basic transportation, such as a bicycle or cab fare, and a modest apartment or small home.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpFirst\">Your occupation also provides access to any resources and facilities required. However, these assets are likely not controlled by you and come with restrictions.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpMiddle\">You can choose an elevated lifestyle, but this comes with responsibilities and obligations to maintain it—if you galivant around the world you are likely to lose the source of your lifestyle.</p><p class=\"NormalSecondCxSpLast\">If you choose a lifestyle uncommon for your occupation provide an explanation for it.</p><h2>Comfortable</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Comfortable occupations have a nicer home, a modest automobile or motorcycle, and enough extra cash for a night out or travel as necessary (but not for any significant length of time or frequency).</p><p class=\"NormalSecond\">Common for Antiquarian, Archeologist, Athlete, Detective/PI, Engineer, Military Officer, Pilot, Professional, Professor, Psychoanalyst, Scientist.</p><h2>Wealthy</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Wealthy occupations have an estate (either city or country), a second home (opposite their estate), vehicles as preferred, and cash as needed. This level of wealth comes with a certain level of notoriety.</p><p class=\"NormalSecond\">Common for Dilettante, Doctor of Medicine, Entertainer, Heir, Lawyer.</p>","value":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.nova6-beyond-hope-and-reason.mm7Q9XEB9HMiBGf7"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"nova6","systemVersion":"0.1.20","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1670794545750,"modifiedTime":1673855982526,"lastModifiedBy":"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY"},"ownership":{"default":0,"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Q1XbgDaCBoyN2RNA"}
{"name":"Instrument","type":"asset","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":"<div style=\"mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\nmso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 0in 1.0pt 0in\"><p class=\"ThemepackHeader2\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:7.0pt;\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><em>Something required for a favored skill</em></span></p></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-no-proof:yes\">This asset is critical to the use of your most important skill.</span></p>","value":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.nova6-beyond-hope-and-reason.WdZjYB4ErTiTcXiv"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"nova6","systemVersion":"0.1.20","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1670794424264,"modifiedTime":1673855971904,"lastModifiedBy":"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY"},"ownership":{"default":0,"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"ScbBeadSEaT5n6wp"}
{"name":"Stability","type":"aspect","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":"<p><em>Replaces Motivation</em></p><hr><p>Your stability is a person, place, activity, or state that enables you to recover when you’ve seen and experienced things beyond what you can handle. Exposure to your stability can help you alleviate dread, recover from mental stress, and overcome grave aspects. Your stability is also a vulnerability—threats to it can instill dread, cause mental stress, or worse.</p>","text":"","label":"Stability","invoked":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.nova6-beyond-hope-and-reason.0RGrPgcX2i4x5ITs"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"nova6","systemVersion":"0.1.20","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1670793787229,"modifiedTime":1673855977846,"lastModifiedBy":"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY"},"ownership":{"default":0,"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"c43qgpp0LOyUGRGo"}
{"name":"Solace","type":"asset","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":"<div style=\"mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\nmso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 0in 1.0pt 0in\"><p class=\"ThemepackHeader2\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:7.0pt;\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><em>Link to your strength and Stability</em></span></p></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\">This asset connects you to your stability and allows you to recover when away from it. Your solace is usually a picture, a symbol, an artifact of an activity, or a trigger of an addiction.</p>","value":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.world.nova6-beyond-hope-and-reason.TLd1zCyn4GpjaBoL"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"nova6","systemVersion":"0.1.20","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1670794478805,"modifiedTime":1673855976165,"lastModifiedBy":"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY"},"ownership":{"default":0,"mUZNOfrfzp75tOoY":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"eZ870UycE9Ah2fTF"}
